Rating: 4
Delicious! I love chocolate so I used 1 1/2 c flour and 3/4 c cocoa powder. Another change I would make in the future is using only PB chips and no chocolate chips, since I thought there could be more peanutty flavor. These cookies are wonderful and I will definitely make them again. My friends commented that they were a good compromise between cookies and brownies since they were so rich. The recipe made about 24 medium-size cookies.

